{"tid":242650,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"濕 滑 阿 嬌 微 博 自 嘲 承 認 自 己 非 常 黑","createTime":"2017-05-14T05:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T10:13:18.000Z","uid":97606,"like":87,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de643017a0075a14b3b268c46c91a6f780ca4171","tid":242650,"uid":97606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:39:05.000Z","msg":"鍾欣桐（阿嬌）呢幾日返咗嚟香港，可以享受吓家庭樂，點知噚日一早佢就遇上倒霉事。阿嬌喺微博留言話：「今天早上在家的大堂因為地板很濕就滑到了，還撞到舊患，整個人躺了在地上動不到，管理員很久才走過來問我有沒有事，我說有呀，他問我能不能站起來，但他卻沒有任何想幫忙扶我起來的行動，連一句對不起都沒有，今天真倒霉。」管理員見到靚女跌親都唔第一時間扶起佢，又真係唔識得憐香惜玉。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20120416/large/16ec5p14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20120416%2Flarge%2F16ec5p14.jpg&h=b885e68f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea95cffa9e6b75d61b4987b96cb4d2c1d1d8e1cd","tid":242650,"uid":56716,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:42:34.000Z","msg":"點解要管理員同佢講對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57cfef142f488a79a6bd6e4b3278ddcc2afee6be","tid":242650,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:43:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要管理員同佢講對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2d6d94a20a853fa6233ce011514b7f89d14e05b0","tid":242650,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:30:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解要管理員同佢講對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c482009d92d04d3132cefb90b0a3b6b5a4f45094","tid":242650,"uid":77753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:36:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54bd92bbe12cfc91b981085a48d98c6dc91ee1e2","tid":242650,"uid":7846,"like":